nodes.text: Voon Massa was a Duros Admiral of the New Republic Defense Fleet. After the Battle of Endor, Admiral Massa was placed at the command of the Fourth Fleet. Tasked to reconquer the Corellian Run, he was victorious at Druckenwell, Milagro, Spirana and Denon. Voon Massa was killed at the Battle of Denon but this decisive victory allowed the New Republic to penetrate the Colonies.
